      """
      WITH null AS a
      OPTIONAL MATCH p = (a)-[r]->()
      RETURN length(nodes(p)), type(r), nodes(p), relationships(p)
      """
    Then the result should be:
      | length(nodes(p)) | type(r) | nodes(p) | relationships(p) |
      | null             | null    | null     | null    |
    And no side effects

